在寒冷的冬天不可開空調（暖氣），除非室內溫度降到3&deg;C以下。簡直像是對中國人的酷刑。<br />\n<br />\n史密斯最後表示，澳洲的商品幾十年來深受中國人的喜愛。或許中國政府這波愚蠢的操作，能讓中國懂得尊重澳洲，重啟政府間溝通的管道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201227/KGTATJIVYBHIRCRYOTVAJFUARA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201227%2FKGTATJIVYBHIRCRYOTVAJFUARA%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=ed7e4f64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201227%2FKGTATJIVYBHIRCRYOTVAJFUARA%2F&h=81893c00\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201227/KGTATJIVYBHIRCRYOTVAJFUARA/</a><br />\n<br />\nSky News:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6217066402001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skynews.com.au%2Fdetails%2F_6217066402001&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=8faf1aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6217066402001</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"講真，天然資源既野，你大陸唔要，大把國家爭住要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}